Package: tp-sdkman-java
Version: 1.0.1
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: curl, zip, unzip
Maintainer: Technical Platform <noreply@example.com>
Description: SDKMAN with Java 25 for Technical Platform WSL
 This package installs SDKMAN and Java 25 (Temurin) for all users.
 SDKMAN is a tool for managing parallel versions of multiple SDKs.
 Java 25 (Eclipse Temurin) is pre-installed and set as default.
